-- MOVES-Former UBS senior exec Christian Hess joins Investec
-- By Anet Josline Pinto in Bangalore
-- Wed Oct 15, 2014 10:12AM EDT
-- None



Oct 15 (Reuters) - Investec Specialist Bank, a division of investment bank and asset manager Investec <INLJ.J> <INVP.L>, said it appointed Christian Hess as head of its newly created financial sponsor transaction group.

He was a founder member of UBS Financial Sponsor Group and the founder of Hess & Co Capital Advisors, Investec said.